.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, car, helicopter, taxi
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, thriller, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, chinese, indonesian, italian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the australian##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 6. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
 7. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the australian##7
 8. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
11. the chinese is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Transport          | train   | helicopter       | taxi    | car      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel | crime         | thriller   |
| Nationality   | italian   | australian  | chinese       | indonesian |
| Sport         | golf      | volleyball  | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

