.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, designer, project-manager, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, martial-arts, zombie
There are 4 different nationalities: german, polish, russian, spanish
There 4 different types of food: plum, pineapple, eggplant, grapefruit
 1. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 2. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere between the bartender and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
 3. the designer is the polish##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
 5. the german is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 6. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 7. the project-manager is not the person watching crime movies##6
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the social-worker##6
 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the designer is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
12. the russian is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Job           | social-worker | bartender | designer | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | zombie    | crime    | martial-arts    |
| Nationality   | german        | spanish   | polish   | russian         |
| Food           | pineapple          | plum       | grapefruit   | eggplant           |

