.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, soy-milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: banana, broccoli, cabbage, spinach
House: tower, cape-cod, palace, victorian
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, ship, trike
 1. the palace house is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating cabbage##1
 3. the person eating banana is not the victorian house##6
 4. the person eating cabbage is not the person drinking milk##6
 5. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
 7. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the trike##7
10. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
11. the victorian house is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person eating spinach##7
13. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the tower house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | milk      | tea      | soy-milk |
| Food          | cabbage     | spinach   | banana   | broccoli |
| House   | palace      | tower | cape-cod | victorian  |
| Transport     | ship        | trike     | roller   | jet-ski  |

