 4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is not the owner of the goldfish##6
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating pear##7
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 9. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
10. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating lemon##1
12. the person eating lemon is not the owner of the hamster##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk   | tea     | mirinda   | iced-tea |
| Food       | pear   | apricot | artichoke | lemon    |
| City      | london | hamburg | edinburgh   | boston  |
| Pet        | rabbit | cat     | hamster   | goldfish |

